Paper: hep-th/0105081

Date: 2001-05-09

Title: Proof of Polyakov conjecture for general elliptic singularities

Authors: Luigi Cantini, Pietro Menotti, Domenico Seminara

Comments: 13 pages latex, to appear in Phys. Lett. B

Journal-ref: Phys.Lett. B517 (2001) 203-209

A proof is given of Polyakov conjecture about the accessory parameters of theSU(1,1) Riemann-Hilbert problem for general elliptic singularities on theRiemann sphere. Its relevance to 2+1 dimensional gravity is stressed.